Changes for 2.1.2 'Tesseract':
----------------------------

Initial release of librist, a fast and portable implementation of the Video Services Forum (VSF) Technical Recommendations TR-06-1 and TR-06-2.
 - Support for all features of the TR-06-1, i.e. Simple Profile
 - Partial support for TR-06-2 including:
   - PSK Encryption, AES 128 and 256
   - Each side can initiate the connection
   - Multipath is supported, load balanced or redundant, i.e. bonding of internet links
   - One sender to many receivers, i.e. media server mode
   - Tested packet recovery up to 50% continuous
   - Sender to receiver jitter will not affect the output
